                    <strong>“BlazorERP Showcase”</strong> is a demonstration ERP-style application written in modern .NET. It highlights <strong>full-stack development using Blazor</strong> for the front end, <strong>Entity Framework Core</strong> for data access, and a responsive component library via <strong>MudBlazor</strong> Key features include:
